    <text>
        <body>
            <p rend="align(right)">
                <placeName>Baltimore</placeName>
                <date>Novr 3<hi rend="sup">rd</hi> 1835</date>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">Dear <addressee>Isaac</addressee></p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">I recd per <persName>Mr Levy</persName> the almanack he and
                    <persName>Mr Peixotto</persName> will<lb/> Leave this at 12 oclock I
                    <sic>supose</sic> paper is scarce that you could<lb/> not send me a Line we are
                all well. I am glad you did <add>?</add><lb/> at <persName>Morris</persName> wedding
                tho others may say what they please. I am glad<lb/>
                <persName>minah</persName> is gone hope she will be better by the time she
                comes<lb/> to <placeName><sic>charlestown</sic></placeName> Aunt <persName>Mrs
                    Depass</persName>
                <persName>Abby</persName> and all your friends send <sic>there</sic><lb/> love to
                you and to all our worthy friend the <persName>Peixottos</persName> tell
                    <persName>Mrs<lb/> Simah</persName> we are all in hopes to see her shortly here,
                if she deserves<lb/> a patch I will give her one so she must come and fetch it
                soon</p>
            <p>I am your friend <hi rend="indent(1)"><persName role="author">Zalma
                    Rehine</persName></hi></p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">remember me to <persName>Mrs Bet. Hart</persName> and all my old
                acquaintance</p>
        </body>
